age\">Message:</p><progress id=\"upload1progress\" max=\"100\" value=\"0\" class=\"childProgress\"></progress></div></td></tr><tr><td><label for=\"upload5\" class=\"uploadButton\">Upload 5</label><input type=\"file\" accept=\".mp4, .webm\" id=\"upload5\" class=\"fileTrigger\"></td><td><video class=\"previewVideo\" id=\"upload5video\" controls></video><div id=\"upload5info\" class=\"info\"><p class=\"childMessage\">Message:</p><progress id=\"upload1progress\" max=\"100\" value=\"0\" class=\"childProgress\"></progress></div></td></tr></tbody></table><br><br><label for=\"devMode\"><input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"devMode\"><span> Enable Dev Mode (Do not enable unless instructed to do so)</span></label><br><br><p class=\"devDebug\" id=\"debugMessage\">Debug message:</p><div id=\"imageContainer\" class=\"devDebug\"></div></div></div>"
